readme:
mapbox-studio-pro-fonts
=======================

Fonts for use with Mapbox Studio. Copyright and licensing information for each font is included in each folder.

### Monotype Imaging (MI) Arial Unicode

Fonts from MI. The license covers use of these fonts for Mapbox Studio only.

### FontFont (FF) fonts

Fonts from FF. The license covers use of these fonts for Mapbox Studio only.
